column12:
'desc': [u'

Sonata Sona Sitara Analog Watch - For Women (Gold) Price: Rs.1599

Key Features

  • Golden Strap
  • Stainless Steel Back Case
  • Water Resistant
  • Contemporary Dial

From the highly popular and prominent watchmakers Sonata comes this ultra-elegant women’s watch that belongs to the Sona Sitara range of designer timepieces. As an ideal choice of personal timekeepers for the modern day woman
column13: this Sona Sitara series watch from Sonata instils in its wearer a sense of poise and grace while also giving great flaunt value. A perfect accessory to flaunt on dressy occasions
column14: this chic timepiece gels perfectly with any of the multitude of dresses that you have gathered over time in your wardrobe. Wear this beautiful analog watch and win the hearts of men at any party or social event; accessorised with the right clothes
column15:
this watch will transform you into a diva.

Body & Design

\r\n\tThis specialised women\u2019s timepiece features a very contemporary dial that is crafted with precision and is an epitome of elegance. This highly creative and innovative dial is designed to fit in a diagonal form rather than your standard round or box dials. The inside of the dial features a watch face that has a smooth design with serene colours. The watch features only four digit markers which are indicated by carefully placed individual crystals in the 12
column18:
and 9 o\u2019clock positions.

\r\n\tThe all-important metal strap on this watch follows the basic form and contour of the dial and goes all the way around
column19: which keeps this highly fashionable watch firmly attached to your wrist at all times. The first strap link on either side of the dial features an extensive arrangement of eye-catching crystals
column20:
making it as much of a fashion accessory as it is a personal timekeeper.
\r\n\t\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0\xa0
Functions and Other Features

\r\n\tThe stylish look of the fashionable timepiece is complemented by its superlative performance. Designed to resist water up to a depth of 30 m
column21: this Sonata watch is enabled to withstand minimal splashing of water. You can let go of your fears while wearing this watch before stepping out of your house during the monsoon. Contemporary and fashionable
column22:
this Sonata analog watch for women is a perfect accessory for the new-age women who define their existence through their poise.

\n
\n ']

A woman’s dress watch should always look elegant and be of a modest size that is right for a woman’s wrist. This Sonata Yuva analog watch for women is what you want to wear with your casuals to the next party or that special function.

Body and Design

Sporting round dial with a stylish design on it
column13: this watch has three hands indicating the hour
column14:
minute and second of the day. This dial is set in a sturdy case with a crystal that has an interesting chiseled shape to it. The watch can be fastened to your hand with an attractive leather strap that complements the watch face. The watch hands can be adjusted to the current time with the rotating crown found on the right side of the watch case.

Functions and Other Features

This analog watch has a mature and elegant design to it and that just might be the reason to add it to your collection of watches you only sport on special occasions. This charming timepiece is also water resistant up to a depth of 30 m. So you won’t have to worry about water seeping in to stop the watch from functioning normally the next time you forget to take your watch off while washing dishes or from an accidental water spill. column12: 'desc': [u'<div class="item_left_column" id="description">\n        <h3 class="item_desc_title fk-uppercase">DKNY Essentials Analog Watch  - For Women (Silver
column13:
Gold) Price: Rs.6495

Key Features

  • Contemporary Dial
  • Golden and Silver Strap
  • Water Resistant
  • Jewelry Clasp
  • Stainless Steel Case

Elegant watches with excellent functionalities exemplify the Essentials collection from DKNY. Their stylish design is matched by the comfy features that these watches are equipped with.

Exemplifying great craftsmanship and eye-catching aesthetics is this exquisitely created women’s analog timepiece from the designer house of DKNY or Donna Karan New York
column14: one of the most reputed international designer brands in the world. Belonging to their ever popular Essentials series of women\'s analog watches
column15: this watch is a perfect choice for the modern day woman who loves to have fun
column16:
party and stand out in a crowd.

\r\n\tThe timekeeping function on this DKNY women\u2019s watch operates using the popular quartz crystal technology. This process works by generating an electrical charge which causes the crystals to vibrate thousand times a second
column17: making them extremely stable resonators for accurate timekeeping. In short
column18:
the battery-powered timepiece will never disappoint you with timekeeping.

Body and Design

\r\n\tThis highly stylized DKNY Essentials Analog Watch - For Women is built around a tonneau shaped dial that contains a watch face with a light-coloured background over which we find the two main watch hands that carry a bright and shiny metallic finish. Even the hour markers
column19:
which are depicted by small rectangular bars carry a similar metallic finish as the watch hands. This clever use of metallic elements against a light background not only adds to the style of the dial but also gives you clear and undisturbed reading of the dial.

\r\n\tThis thoughtfully conceived dial is enveloped by a very aesthetic stainless steel case that is designed to offer the dial considerable protection against impacts and shocks. Keeping this attractive dial comfortably attached to your wrist is the watch\u2019s extremely stylish two-toned stainless steel bracelet strap that operates like a jewellery clasp. The links on the strap are adjustable
column20: thus allowing you to change the length of the strap according to your convenience. The dial is capped with a highly durable and scratch-resistant mineral glass cover
column21:
which gives the dial the all-important sheen too.

Functions and Other Features

\r\n\tBeauty
column22: as they say
column23: is skin deep and this DKNY analog women\u2019s watch adheres to this principle in toto. The stylish looks of this timepiece are balanced by efficient functionalities. Crafted to withstand splashes of water up to a depth of 30 m
column24: this DKNY watch qualifies as your ideal companion for spending a lazy Sunday aside the club pool. Contemporary and exquisite
column25:
the DKNY Essentials analog watch is a perfect tribute to the modern woman who defines her existence through her poise.

\n
\n ']

Mother nature is the personification of a woman's true beauty. She is nurturing and loving and alway seeks balance. Sonata
column13: a leading watches brand in India
column14: has created a watch that has been truly inspired by nature. Like the gentle ripples that stir a still lake to life when the raindrops kiss its gentle cheek
column15:
the rippled body of the Sonata Yuva Gold watch glistens with charming elegance.\xa0

The watch has been designed for every woman. Perfect to wear with your formal wear at the office this watch asserts a calm confidence and grabs the attention of your colleagues. The watch can also be paired with a lovely dress when you go out with your husband for a romantic dinner. The watch drapes your femininity in sheer splendor.

Body and Design

The Sonata watch has a softly coloured round dial that is dotted with elegant time markers and three display hands. The time markers also have been set to resemble how the ripples begin to amplify. The dial is held in the beautiful metallic case that gleams like the morning dew. The case has a metallic finish that makes the watch look stunning on your wrist. The uniquely shaped lugs of the watch serve the dual purpose of being decorative and of holding the case on the sleek leather strap. The watch sits firmly on your wrist thanks to the secure buckle clasp.

Functions and Other Features

The Sonata watch isn’t merely an accessory that can be paired with your clothes
column16: it is a timekeeper that ticks steadfastly by your side all day
column17: everyday. Along with strength and durability

Providing you with elegance and style
column15:
this watch from Sonata can be worn with all your casual wear to college or work. Team this trendy watch with your fashionable kurtis and stylish T-shirts and make an enormous style statement wherever you go.

Body and Design

The watch has a youthful and vibrant design that is sure to make you stand out in a crowded party where you are in a room full of people. The watch is built around an impressively crafted round dial which gives the watch a graceful and refined finish. Plain and simple
column16: the watch face comes with an uncluttered design that makes it easier for you to read time with precision. The seconds
column17: minutes and hour hand are provided with a rich metallic finish
column18:
while the digits on the watch are furnished with deep contrasting colours against the light background of the watch. Use of bright and vivid colours enhances the watch’s aesthetic value and gives it a classy look and feel. The highly attractive dial of the watch is steadfastly and comfortably fitted to your wrist at all times with the help of a stylish leather strap that is extremely durable.

Functions and Other Features

Apart from the watch’s appealing femininity and lavish design
column19: the watch also provides you with accurate and reliable time reading. This watch from Sonata is water resistant up to a depth of 30 m and is hence
column20: well-protected from accidental spills
column21: moisture gathering or the drizzles you enjoy on a rainy evening. If you are on a lookout for a durable and sophisticated watch that is good for daily use
column22:
this analog watch from Sonata is your perfect choice.
